column7:
What type of commission is this? 

If you've selected an option that is NOT colored sketch, flat colored, cell-shaded, rendered or a ref sheet, you do not need to select an option.
column8: How many characters will be featured?
column9: Will this piece feature a complex background?
column10:
Please drop your ref sheets here for the character(s) in the piece.

If you want a complex background, examples are also appreciated.

Make sure your images are .PNG or high quality .JPEG
column11:
A clear description of what you would like the piece to be about. 

For Headshot Page, please put expressions you would like here.

For Sketch Page, please drop keywords/themes here.

For Reference Sheets, keep descriptions in bullet-point form and simple.
